An ANC ward Councilor in uMkhambathini Mid Illovo in KZN has survived a suspected assassination attempt. Mzwandile Shandu says gunmen opened fire on his home, injuring one person and killing another. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - An ANC ward councillor in uMkhambathini Mid Illovo in KZN has survived a suspected assassination attempt. Mzwandile Shandu says gunmen opened fire on his home, injuring one person and killing another. READ: 11 people killed in Khayelitsha shootings While it's suspected the attack was politically motivated, this is yet to be confirmed. Police say they are still investigating the matter. Watch the video above for more details on this story. 